pathway.author: [Mkutmon, Elisa, Eweitz]

comments.content:
Model depicting mesodermal specification based on the literature and highly enriched gene expression profiles via comparison across dozens of independent induced and embryonic pluripotent stem cell lines, following differentiation to multiple lineages (ectoderm, mesoderm, endoderm, embryoid body). The underlying genomic data can be obtained from: 
https://www.synapse.org/#!Synapse:syn1773109

Developed using Gene Ontology mesoderm process associated genes and interactions from the software NetPerspective (AltAnalyze). A preliminary layout was obtained using the exported SIF file in Cytoscape's Cerebral plugin.
This pathway was inferred from Homo sapiens pathway [http://wikipathways.org/instance/WP2857_r80151 WP2857(80151)]  with a 19.0% conversion rate.
